title: {MomXXX} Jenny Simons {You're So Beautiful} NEW 29 June 2015
description: Jenny was always stunning in her college days as she was a model and athletics guru but now she is even more radiant. Her golden blonde hair simply glows as the light hits every strand and her eyes are alive with excitement and devilish intent. George has always had a soft spot for Jenny, and as he says himself "It's rare to meet someone so beautiful on the outside as well as the inside". The two have a magical sensual electricity between them which is obvious the moment you see them together, and this always leads to the most passionate of love making with both of them reaching new sensual heights together
